<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Our Restaurant</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-image: url('restaurant-banner.jpg'); /* Replace with your image */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #ff5722; /* Vibrant orange */
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .about {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .about h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .about p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .about-image {
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 600px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .services {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .service {
            background-color: #ffe0b2; /* Light orange background */
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 300px;
        }

        .service h3 {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Our Restaurant</h1>
        <p>Experience the finest dining with us!</p>
        <a href="#about" class="btn">Learn More</a>
    </header>

    <section id="about" class="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Our restaurant offers a unique culinary experience with a variety of delicious dishes crafted by our expert chefs. We are committed to using only the freshest ingredients to ensure every bite is a delight.</p>
        <img src="restaurant-interior.jpg" alt="Restaurant Interior" class="about-image"> <!-- Replace with your image -->
    </section>

    <section class="services">
        <div class="service">
            <h3>Fine Dining</h3>
            <p>Enjoy a luxurious dining experience in a sophisticated atmosphere.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service">
            <h3>Takeout & Delivery</h3>
            <p>Convenient options to enjoy your favorite meals at home.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service">
            <h3>Event Catering</h3>
            <p>Let us make your special occasion unforgettable with our catering services.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Our Restaurant. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
